summary: This document is an email chain from July 2020 regarding the filing of an endorsed Order under seal in the case 'In Re: Grand Jury Subpoena_19-mc-00179'. It involves communication with the chambers of Judge Sarah Netburn of the United States District Court for the Southern District of New York.

persons.name: Sarah Netburn

keyFacts: The document pertains to the sealed case 'In Re: Grand Jury Subpoena_19-mc-00179'.
